Quell the Profane	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:Exalted	VISIBLE:YES		PRETOTALAB:8		PREABILITY:2,CATEGORY=FEAT,Power Attack,Resounding Blow									PRESTAT:1,STR=13					PREALIGN:LG,NG,CG				DESC:Whenever you deal a critical hit to an evil creature using a melee weapon with which you are proficient, your opponent must succeed on a Fortitude save (DC 10 + 1/2 your character level + your Cha modifier) or take 1d4+1 points of temporary Strength damage. A monk's unarmed strike is considered a melee weapon for purposes of this feat.																	SOURCEPAGE:BoED						
