Sanctify Weapon	CATEGORY:FEAT	TYPE:Exalted	VISIBLE:YES				PRESPELL:1,Align Weapon														PREALIGN:LG,NG,CG				DESC:When you cast align weapon, the affected weapon also becomes sanctified. A sanctified weapon deals 1 extra point of holy damage to evil creatures or 1d4 points of damage to evil outsiders and evil undead. In addition, creatures with the corrupted template (described in the Book of Vile Darkness) cannot recover hit point damage dealt by a sanctified weapon by means of normal healing, including fast healing.																	SOURCEPAGE:BoED						
